Cookies managing
Cookie Settings
Cookies necessary for the correct operation of the site are always enabled.
Other cookies are configurable.
Essential cookies
Always On. These cookies are essential so that you can use the website and use its functions. They cannot be turned off. They're set in response to requests made by you, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms.
Analytics cookies
Disabled
These cookies collect information to help us understand how our Websites are being used or how effective our marketing campaigns are, or to help us customise our Websites for you. See a list of the analytics cookies we use here.
Advertising cookies
Disabled
These cookies provide advertising companies with information about your online activity to help them deliver more relevant online advertising to you or to limit how many times you see an ad. This information may be shared with other advertising companies. See a list of the advertising cookies we use here.

Transparent Vaults Marketplace for Investors
Investors browse Vaults, review term sheets, and deposit funds, receiving LP tokens representing their share of the Vaults capital.
Breach-Proof Contract
On-chain voting on contractual changes and financial decisions ensures transparency and immutability.
Automatic Decentralized Accounting / Shareholder Registry
Investors receive LP tokens (Smartcoins) upon deposit and burn them upon withdrawal according to the smart contract's rules.

AI Execution for Automatic Vaults
Managers execute trades via delegated calls to the smart contract, using AI-driven strategies to optimize trading activities.
Permissionless Fund Creation
Asset managers or strategy designers can create decentralized funds, specifying strategies and parameters through a user-friendly interface.
Triple Layer Security System & Monitoring
Oracles and smart contract monitoring protect the funds and prevent suspicious activity, including KYT/KYC modules to prevent money laundering.

What does it mean for users
For Investors
Diversification
Performance
Control
Security
For Individual Traders
Efficiency
Error Management
Flexibility

For Strategy Managers
Scalability
Risk Mitigation
Transparency
Automation
Scalability: Managers can handle more strategies efficiently with the help of AI
Risk Mitigation: The AI execution layer continuously assesses risks and adapts strategies, reducing exposure to market volatility
Automation: Routine tasks are automated, allowing managers to focus on higher-level strategic decisions
Transparency: On-chain governance and smart contracts ensure all actions are transparent and immutable, building trust with investors
Security: Traders do not need to expose their private keys, maintaining high security
Flexibility: They can deploy and manage their own strategies without relying on external managers
Efficiency: The AI execution layer helps optimize strategies, providing better performance without manual intervention
Error Management: Pre-defined rules manage AI hallucinations, ensuring reliable and accurate execution
Diversification: Investors can choose from a variety of vaults managed by experts or AI, diversifying their portfolio
Control: Investors retain control over their funds through LP tokens, participating in decision-making processes
Security: Funds are protected by smart contracts and vaults' pre-defined rules, eliminating the risk of mismanagement or fraud
Performance: AI-driven strategies optimize returns by leveraging real-time data and analytics, enhancing investment performance
